yes and one on no all five said they didnt know much about souter 
there remain too many unanswered questions about who he is and 
how this nomination came about said peter flaherty chairman of 
the conservative campaign fund former chairman of citizens for 
reagan and the one who said no this man has been on the planet 
for 50 years never given a speech written an article 
robert grant president of the american freedom coalition said 
all he knows about souter is what he read in the paper theres a 
