whatever he wanted them to do west said durenberger if 
asked has been saying that he would just as soon they accept it as 
he has done 
durenberger would be the seventh senator to be censured 
condemned or denounced in the 20th century the senates most 
severe punishment for a member short of expulsion according to 
senate historians 
