last week relations between the two governments hit a low point 
spain withdrew its ambassador and suspended a 25 million aid 
program cuba said spain should not have allowed the 18 to remain 
because they were not suffering political persecution 
cuba has called for the voluntary and unconditional 
departure of the cubans at the embassy spain has said it will not 
