marijuana smoke 
benjamin said he became suspicious when passengers on the boat 
made repeated trips below decks but said he could not see what 
they were doing and was not interested in trying to find out 
i had suspicions that there was something out of the ordinary 
going on on that boat benjamin said i saw all of them going 
below decks quite repeatedly 
